{icon:bullet,1.2} {c_label}1点：{/c} {c_number}{payload:DAMAGE_TOOLTIP_1CP}{/c} 点伤害, {c_number}[{SF_10}|%+|]{/c} 几率
{icon:bullet,1.2} {c_label}2点：{/c} {c_number}{payload:DAMAGE_TOOLTIP_2CP}{/c} 点伤害, {c_number}[{SF_10}*2|%+|]{/c} 几率
{icon:bullet,1.2} {c_label}3点：{/c} {c_number}{payload:DAMAGE_TOOLTIP_3CP}{/c} 点伤害, {c_number}[{SF_15}*{SF_10}*3|%+|]{/c} 几率{/if}
